span>Scope of this document:</span></h2>
<p><strong>In scope:</strong></p>
<p><span>Channel changes</span></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span>&nbsp;to <strong>make</strong> a DE payment with the existing POS=
T /Payments endpoint</span>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span>UI mapping / EXP API mapping</span></li>
<li><span>BSB Eligibility service changes to support DE method</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Out of scope:</strong></p>
<p><span>Uplift to v2 payment initiation</span></p>
<p><span>Listing and details of DE payment ( <span class=3D"jira-issue reso=
lved" data-jira-key=3D"ART-15154"> <a href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.=
au/browse/ART-15154" class=3D"jira-issue-key"><img class=3D"icon" src=3D"ht=
tps://jira.srv.westpac.com.au:8444/secure/viewavatar?size=3Dxsmall&amp;avat=
arId=3D10300&amp;avatarType=3Dissuetype">ART-15154</a> - <span class=3D"sum=
mary">DE Phase 4 - Transaction Listing / Detail / Payment Listing / Detail =
for DE (Customer and Staff)</span> <span class=3D"aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-s=
ubtle             aui-lozenge-success
     jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Done</span> </span> )&nbsp;</span>=
</p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:MakingaDEPayment[ERM24E4Aug2024]-KeyDecisions"><span>Key=
 Decisions</span></h2>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped relative-table confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 80.=
485954%;" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers" data-snooker-locked-cols=3D"0=
">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 1.415094%;">
<col style=3D"width: 47.0283%;">
<col style=3D"width: 36.650944%;">
<col style=3D"width: 14.858491%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh" scope=3D"col" contenteditable=3D=
"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false"><br></th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Decision</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Outcome</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">By</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Do we introduce a new endpoint for DE payments o=
n the EXP api and Payment Initiation API since this follows a new PAIN001 v=
ersion</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">No, Payment Initiation API V1 can map the existi=
ng version of the schema to the 10x version. No new endpoint needed</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M061387" =
href=3D"/display/~M061387" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1359044573" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Thomas Van Deun</a> , <a clas=
s=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062091" href=3D"/d=
isplay/~M062091" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1504078445" data-linked-resourc=
e-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"htt=
ps://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Amandeep Singh</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Do we always show DE payment method in dropdown =
list incase it is allowed based on BSB Service level lookup (this would mea=
n alongside the highest priority NPP method)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>See <span class=3D"jira-issue resolved" data-jira-key=3D"ART-39187"> <a =
href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/ART-39187" class=3D"jira-iss=
ue-key"><img class=3D"icon" src=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au:8444/ima=
ges/icons/issuetypes/story.svg">ART-39187</a> - <span class=3D"summary">(US=
) [DE3] Uplift Payment Details (input details) Page - DE UI</span> <span cl=
ass=3D"aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle             aui-lozenge-success
     jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Done</span> </span></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M061387" =
href=3D"/display/~M061387" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1359044573" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Thomas Van Deun</a> &nbsp;</p=
>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">3</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">&nbsp;All Business validation happens in 10x and=
 we handle RJCT accordingly in the UI. (Eg available funds, account state w=
ont be check in channels)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Agreed</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M061387" =
href=3D"/display/~M061387" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1359044573" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Thomas Van Deun</a> , Ellen</=
