n</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:MakingaDEPayment[ERM24E4Aug2024]-GalaxyPaymentChanges:">=
Galaxy Payment Changes:</h2>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers=
" data-snooker-locked-cols=3D"0">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh" scope=3D"col" contenteditable=3D=
"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false"><br></th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Change</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Summary</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Details</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Allow for Payment Method DE - uplift to servi=
ce level lookup</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">The Service Level Lookup endpoint will now retur=
n DE eligibility. The EXP API logic needs to be updated to allow DE method =
to be returned alongside the current prioritisation for Fast Payment / Osko=
.</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/03.+SD%3A+Lookup+Sch=
eme+eligibility+for+BSBs">03. SD: Lookup NPP Business Services for BSB's</a=
> <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">(Not updated yet - 19/02/2025)</span=
></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Filter out input fields and change validation=
 rules&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Certain description input fields are not applica=
ble in a DE scenario. The UI needs to hide them and not send them with the =
API request to the EXP when a DE payment is submitted.&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Covered in the user stories:&nbsp; <span class=3D"jira-issue resolved" d=
ata-jira-key=3D"ART-17026"> <a href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/brow=
se/ART-17026" class=3D"jira-issue-key"><img class=3D"icon" src=3D"https://j=
ira.srv.westpac.com.au:8444/images/icons/issuetypes/epic.svg">ART-17026</a>=
 - <span class=3D"summary">DEL: DE3 - Portal uplift to capture and submit D=
E payments</span> <span class=3D"aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle            =
 aui-lozenge-success
     jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Done</span> </span></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">3</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">UI - EXP API POST /payments mapping update&nbsp;=
</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>New fields need to be send to exp api when DE=
 is selected</p><p>Some fields need to be added to the EXP API swagger</p><=
p><br></p><p>All the fields need to be hooked up to the CAP API integration=
 (but naming of the values is the same, so its a 1:1 mapping)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span><a href=3D"/pages/viewpage.action?pageI=
d=3D1946687460">Make a Payment / Transfer UI - EXP API Mapping [ERM 25E4 - =
August 2025]</a></span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">4</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Handle new errorstatus reasons</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>All the validation will happen in 10x, so we =
can expect:</p><p style=3D"text-align: left;">&nbsp;201: ACSC or RJCT</p><p=
 style=3D"text-align: left;">202: PNDG and ACSP</p><p style=3D"text-align: =
left;"><br></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;">For RJCT there will be new co=
des, analysis TBC on which ones we need to show</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>TBC</span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
